data.description: Welcome to this meticulously maintained home, built in 2018, nestled on a generous corner lot that combines modern living with comfort and style. Spanning 1,848 square feet of living space, this residence is a perfect blend of elegance and functionality, designed to cater to the needs of today's homeowners and offering easy access to Lackland Air Force Base.    As you step inside, you're greeted by an open concept layout with high ceilings that enhance the sense of space and light. The heart of the home is the stunning kitchen, boasting sleek black appliances, beautiful white quartz countertops, and an abundance of cabinets and counter space. This open kitchen is a chef's delight and makes entertaining a breeze, seamlessly flowing into the living and dining areas.    The home features durable tile and laminate flooring throughout the downstairs, creating a cohesive and easy-to-maintain living environment. Upstairs, new carpet adds warmth and comfort, leading you to the home's private quarters. All bedrooms are conveniently located upstairs, including the large primary bedroom, which serves as a peaceful retreat with its ample size and en-suite primary bath adorned with beautiful tile work in the shower.    An additional highlight is the versatile loft space, enhanced with extra outlets, making it an ideal spot for computer workstations, gaming, or a cozy reading nook. This flex space adds valuable living area that can be tailored to your lifestyle needs.    The thoughtful upgrades extend outside, where the seller has added a high-quality extended covered patio. This outdoor haven features a privacy barrier, lights, fan, and plumbing rough-in for a future outdoor kitchen, offering the perfect setting for relaxation and entertaining.    For added convenience, the refrigerator, washer, and dryer will all convey to the new owner, making this home move-in ready.    Located in a vibrant San Antonio neighborhood with easy access to Lackland Air Force Base, this home is a true gem, offering both privacy and proximity to local amenities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful house your new home, where every detail has been carefully considered for your comfort and enjoyment.
